{
  "stem": "13471.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was-- walked over to the window, and I was looking out there, and I was smoking a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, she said, after I put my cigarette out, I turned around, and  you know what?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She said, all my reading lamps were gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I bet you I know what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, you go back to your room, and let me handle it from here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I called Wally in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, Wally, look, boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, you've got to take those lamps back to those people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, but they're limeys, Commander, they're limeys!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, yep, but they're limeys on our side, boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Then he goes-- but that-- now, he-- as I say, he-- and one of the other things that he could-- that we couldn't get was typewriters.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that scoundrel, he stomped around, and somewhere he found out that there was an entire warehouse in Munich full of typewriters-- German typewriters.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the owner was holding them out, waiting for better market conditions before letting them go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, all we needed to know was that they were in that warehouse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then we could get military government, you see, to move in and grab them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, Wally was simply invaluable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I used to give-- the only thing we could do there was give parties.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was no amusement.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was-- it would be my turn to give a party, and so I would call Wally and say, Wally, I'm going to have 35 people out at the house for a Friday-night party.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said, take care of it and get things organized for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I get home from the Justizpalast about 5:30, and there'd be a three-piece German band tuning up.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
